2 1 2 3

smart handling of unsorted RST headers

the RST format deducts header levels from the order headers are presented in the document. as a result a sequence of headers with levels 2, 1, 2, 3

some of the documents in pandoc-pdf still present fatal errors when
translating to HTML, migrate our process from samples to full
documents in this sense, linee-guida-esercenti.rst present issue
pandoc-test#4 (test2) which was closed. the malformed document
prevents any HTML to be produced. it would be way better to simply add
headers in the right order saying "header 1 by pandoc", "header 2 by
pandoc" etcetera, referring to a documentation page

l'obiettivo é collezionare documenti in un unico index.rst
diviso per sezioni o capitoli
ogni file corrisponderà ad un sito
ogni cosa ben tradotta da pandoc evita lavoro manuale tedioso
